docs.abstract: After poor box-office numbers for Mindy Kaling’s “Late Night,” the company shrank its ambitious release plan for a big fall movie, “The Aeronauts.”
docs.snippet: After poor box-office numbers for Mindy Kaling’s “Late Night,” the company shrank its ambitious release plan for a big fall movie, “The Aeronauts.”
docs.lead_paragraph: LOS ANGELES — “The Aeronauts,” an adventure film about swashbuckling 19th-century hot-air balloonists, was built for the big screen. Led by an Oscar winner, Eddie Redmayne, and a “Star Wars” star, Felicity Jones, it has real cinematic sweep, with sequences that take place miles above sea level. In May, Amazon Studios announced that the movie would play exclusively on IMAX screens for a one-week engagement before “a full theatrical run.”

headline.main: Behind Amazon’s Sudden Change in Its Film Strategy
headline.print_headline: Amazon Downsizes Its Ambitions For Cinema

docs.abstract: The E.U.’s top antitrust regulator ordered Broadcom to halt specific practices while the bloc investigates possible anticompetitive activity.
docs.snippet: The E.U.’s top antitrust regulator ordered Broadcom to halt specific practices while the bloc investigates possible anticompetitive activity.
docs.lead_paragraph: European authorities took an even more aggressive approach than usual to regulating the technology industry Wednesday when they applied a rarely used rule, ordering a company to halt a potentially anticompetitive practice while an investigation is underway.

headline.main: Europe’s Margrethe Vestager Takes a Rare Step Toward Big Tech
headline.print_headline: E.U. Regulator Will Rein In Broadcom During Antitrust Inquiry

docs.abstract: Wherein our columnist gives up on shopping and lets Amazon’s Personal Shopper dress her for fall.
docs.snippet: Wherein our columnist gives up on shopping and lets Amazon’s Personal Shopper dress her for fall.
docs.lead_paragraph: This is a retail review in which I do not leave my apartment. All of the movements and decisions described take place in my mind or on my phone. Where mind ends and phone begins is sometimes unclear. All you have to know is that wherever I am, I am shopping.

docs.abstract: Attorney General Xavier Becerra is in Google and Facebook’s backyard. But unlike nearly all other state attorneys general, he won’t say whether he’s investigating them.

docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — When numerous state attorneys general gathered last month on the steps of the Supreme Court to announce an antitrust investigation into Google, one was conspicuously absent: Xavier Becerra, California’s attorney general.

docs.abstract: Members of Congress questioned whether the power of Facebook, Google, Apple and Amazon could hurt consumer privacy.

docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — House lawmakers on Friday pressed experts on how the market power of major tech platforms could hurt consumer privacy, showing that an antitrust investigation into Facebook, Google, Apple and Amazon is growing to include deeper questions about their business models.
